source.name: Patent Grant Maintenance Fee Events (1981 - Present)
source.description: Contains recorded maintenance fee events for patents granted from September 1, 1981 - Present. Each new weekly file is cumulative. The file format is ASCII. This product includes a MaintFeeEvents.zip file for each week (cumulative). Within each weekly zip file is: MaintFeeEvents_yyyymmdd.txt  where "yyyymmdd" is a Monday. Approximately 70 MB.
